  "detailed_description": "Limbs is a one to two player dexterity game where you take control over the limbs of a string puppet. Immerse yourself in a handcrafted world where moving each limb individually makes for challenging but rewarding and hilarious gameplay. Playfully swing, jump and manually walk as best as you can through a knackered kingdom while progressing through a story inspired by puppet theater storytelling.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2>Control two limbs at a time: In single player you switch the control between arms and legs, while in two player mode both players take control over one arm and one leg.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/f49d7df0553160e936c543cfc94c21f4.poster.avif?t=1731410621\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/f49d7df0553160e936c543cfc94c21f4.webm?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/f49d7df0553160e936c543cfc94c21f4.mp4?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Make your limbs work together to master a unique gameplay loop: Even if the tasks you perform would be easy in another game, the coordinative nature makes them challenging.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/adc3129ebaa32471037c86b4b589e625.poster.avif?t=1731410621\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/adc3129ebaa32471037c86b4b589e625.webm?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/adc3129ebaa32471037c86b4b589e625.mp4?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You choose how to move your character: Just like a real puppeteer all character motions are under your control.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/ce4cf40dd7a62ef815db55247cd68abf.poster.avif?t=1731410621\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/ce4cf40dd7a62ef815db55247cd68abf.webm?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/ce4cf40dd7a62ef815db55247cd68abf.mp4?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Intuitive cooperative gameplay: After a while players start to get in tune with each other and perform actions together even without communicating verbally.",
  "about_the_game": "Limbs is a one to two player dexterity game where you take control over the limbs of a string puppet. Immerse yourself in a handcrafted world where moving each limb individually makes for challenging but rewarding and hilarious gameplay. Playfully swing, jump and manually walk as best as you can through a knackered kingdom while progressing through a story inspired by puppet theater storytelling.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2>Control two limbs at a time: In single player you switch the control between arms and legs, while in two player mode both players take control over one arm and one leg.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/f49d7df0553160e936c543cfc94c21f4.poster.avif?t=1731410621\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/f49d7df0553160e936c543cfc94c21f4.webm?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/f49d7df0553160e936c543cfc94c21f4.mp4?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Make your limbs work together to master a unique gameplay loop: Even if the tasks you perform would be easy in another game, the coordinative nature makes them challenging.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/adc3129ebaa32471037c86b4b589e625.poster.avif?t=1731410621\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/adc3129ebaa32471037c86b4b589e625.webm?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/adc3129ebaa32471037c86b4b589e625.mp4?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You choose how to move your character: Just like a real puppeteer all character motions are under your control.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/ce4cf40dd7a62ef815db55247cd68abf.poster.avif?t=1731410621\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/ce4cf40dd7a62ef815db55247cd68abf.webm?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/ce4cf40dd7a62ef815db55247cd68abf.mp4?t=1731410621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Intuitive cooperative gameplay: After a while players start to get in tune with each other and perform actions together even without communicating verbally.",
